    "body": "Instead of another script as added in #14607, this adds a simple argument to `spack commands` that updates the completion script.  Developers can now just run:\r\n\r\n```console\r\n    $ spack commands --update-completion\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis should make it simpler for developers to remember to run this *before* the tests fail.  Also, this version tab-completes.",
